The paper deals with the design of a bit allocation method for ADCs in mmWave massive MIMO communication receivers. This involves optimization of the quantization error under a power constraint. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), which deals with the fundamental limits of communication systems. The paper also involves communication system design, which falls under cs.COMM (Networking and Internet Architecture). The use of massive MIMO and analog phased arrays suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of mmWave frequencies suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the use of ADCs suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.NI (Networking and Information Theory).
